        "content": "\nTrivial but untested:\n\n```python\nfrom unittest.mock import patch\nfrom cli import main\n\ndef test_main_passes_dry_run_and_config(monkeypatch):\n    monkeypatch.setattr(\"sys.argv\", [\"cli.py\", \"-c\", \"custom.yaml\", \"--dry-run\"])\n    with patch(\"cli.run_sync\") as run_sync:\n        main()\n    run_sync.assert_called_once_with(\"custom.yaml\", dry_run=True)\n```\n\n---\n\n",
        "level": 3
